All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Account
The class represents account which holds amount of money
Address
The class holds the address information
Administrator
The class allows admins to control playgrounds by activating, suspending or deleting them
eWallet
The class has the responsibility of controlling financial operations in the system
GoFoSystem
The class represents the system that holds all the info
Main  
Player
A class that inherits User, and allows player to book playgrounds and do player functionalities.
Playground
The class stores playgrounds info and operations
PlaygroundOwner
The class that inherits User, and allows an owner to add (own) playgrounds and control them
Team
The class represents a group of players that form a team
TimeSlot
The class represents a slot of time
User
An abstract class (generalization) that holds the common properties between a Player and a Playground Owner
